    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Electroanalytical technique used in analytical chemistry to determine the chemical makeup of small concentrations of metals in a substance by measuring electrical activity on electrodes placed in the substance.</Note_Text>
